ridicule et d'une stupidite affligente il n'y a pas grand chose a dire de plus , sinon que j'etais tout pres de ny lors des attentats . l'auteur de ce livre est a mes yeux ni plus ni moins qu'un charlatant . ||| ridiculous and stupid afflict there is not much more to say except that i was close to ny during the attacks . the author of this book is to my eyes neither more nor less than charlatans .